    "prompt": "A technician wearing advanced data gloves performing a virtual assembly of an intricate aerospace connector within a high-fidelity, immersive 3D simulation of an aircraft cabin section. The scene shows detailed hand movements, glowing virtual components, and real-time visual feedback on a nearby screen.",
    "alt": "中航光电技术人员使用数据手套进行航空连接器虚拟装配培训场景"
  }
}

